Q4.Write a PHP script to accept username and password. If in the first three chances,
username and password entered is correct then display second form with “Welcome
message” otherwise display error message. [Use Session]

Answer::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::

<?php
session_start();
$u=$_POST['uname'];
$p=$_POST['pass'];
if(isset($_SESSION['attempt']))
{
       if($u=="admin" && $p=="bcs123" && $_SESSION['attempt']<=3)
       {
                      echo"Welcome";
        }
        elseif($_SESSION['attempt']<=3)
        {
                  echo"error occured";
                  $_SESSION['attempt']+=1;
        }
        else{
                   echo"reach maximum attempt";
             }
  }
  else
  {
             $_SESSION['attempt']=1;
 }
?>
<html>
<body>
<form method="POST" action="#">
Enter Username:<input type="text" name="uname">
Enter Password:<input type="text" name="pass">
<button type="submit">Submit</button>
</body>
</html>

